name: Cerita-nusantara
tagline: Cerita Nusantara, Indonesian Folk Stories delivered in a fun way.
body: Cerita Nusantara is an android application designed to deliver Indonesian Folk Stories in a fun and accessible way. Cerita Nusantara present tales in form of images, animations, with playable game in between.
